node.text:
…..and this was Soooo emotional for me….thank you God for blessing my company @ellaelisque enough to provide for my family 🥺 I’ve been wanting to do this for years and every time I got close to my goals, HERE COMES THE DEVIL, but guess who’s not grater than my God ? 

I kept getting up and trying AGAIN, and AGAIN, and AGAIN until I HIT. It ain’t NO fun making this kind of money and my momma still working, I’ve only been relaunched for 7 months, but the minute I saw it was LIT for @ellaelisque I made SURE my priority was to retire my mother, ( my father is already retired ) … my mother is 69 years old , and been a paralegal for 30 years, I pray this encourages my other fellow entrepreneurs…if business is going good for you, make sure you take care of the people that’s been taking care of you all ya life 🥺🥺❤️❤️

Love, 
Maxie.j

 🎥 @ignaciosgram

node.title: Sooo I retired my mom for mother’s day 🥺😢

node.text:
-

I really thought I was going to a private LV event 😳 I had no idea my man had planned a whole surprise proposal 😭 

all my friends and family kept this secret from me successfully 😩When I hit that corner, I dam near passed out 😭😭😭 I couldnt believe my eyes, I still feel like i’m dreaming 💭 ….

I pray every woman , at some point in their lives , get to experience what it feels like, when a real man to love you 🥺❤️ 

answer your dms sis your future husband might be in there waiting like mine was 😩🤣❤️

( I do not own the rights to this music )

#HeProposed #ISaidYes #issafiancé  #MaxandBenfortheWin

node.text:
Thank you for loving me Benson... it’s been YEARS since I’ve felt this appreciated, loved, and adored. 

You know I LOVE being surprised 😭 it’s just something about a man caring enough to think  it through, plan , and execute....brings me to tears every time.... Icing on the cake: you know how to dress me 😂🙌🏾 A fashion designers DREAM 😫 A man with STYLE and TASTE😫🙌🏾 .....

I love you....1 year down, A life time to go. 

Happy Anniversary ❤️

node.text:
My very first Virtual Fashion Show was a HIT...

stayed true to my brand Identity, from music choice, set choice, to designs, y’all know the vibes 👄😉 .........Every time I watch it I get chills 😫❤️... I worked so hard on this project  y’all have no idea 😓

Who got to watch the show ??? What did y’all think ??? Somebody in the @ellaelisque comments said “ if SHE DAT was a person “ 😂🙌🏾 I love y’all

Everything you see in the show is available for purchase on @ellaelisque site www.EllaeLisque.com ( link in bio )

node.text:
lmao Man i’m crying laughing as I’m reposting this, Benson surprised me with a full day of activities in Mexico, at first I was mad cus this man KNOOOWS me and THIS WIG don’t do no dam hiking or zip lining or ANYTNING that involves sweating! lmao but I was a good sport and said fuck it let me just try, just for this nigga to be the one scared of heights lmao big scary ass ! 😂😂😂 

Get you some one that’ll take you outta your comfort zone and create unforgettable memories ♥️ It’s the best way to grow together. 

Go watch my Mexico trip highlight  in my bio 😂 😂  we a whole fool 😩, it’s already so many of y’all cracking up in my dms too blowing my shit up 😭😭😂😂 Poor Benson ahaha !
